---
import BaseLayout from "src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SearchFilterApp from "src/components/search-filter/SearchFilterApp.tsx";
---

<BaseLayout title="Search & Filter UI â€” Brad Newman">
  <section>
    <h1>Search & Filter UI</h1>
    <p>
      An interactive React project demonstrating state management, component
      composition, and accessible UI patterns.
    </p>

    <SearchFilterApp client:load />
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="technical-notes-heading">
    <h2 id="technical-notes-heading">Technical Notes</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>
        Built with React inside an Astro project to demonstrate framework
        interoperability and selective hydration.
      </li>
      <li>
        Uses controlled inputs and derived state instead of duplicating filtered
        results in state.
      </li>
      <li>
        Accessibility considerations include semantic form grouping, screen
        reader announcements, and keyboard-friendly interactions.
      </li>
      <li>
        UI state is synchronized to URL query parameters to allow bookmarking
        and sharing.
      </li>
      <li>Styles are scoped using CSS Modules to avoid global side effects.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
